    <item>
      <title>中国工厂活动在预期特朗普关税之前扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-factory-activity-expands-before-expected-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的工厂活动在三月份的一年中的最快速度扩大了，这是全球第二经济体的欢迎新闻，此前美国的关税可能会进一步加剧贸易关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-factory-activity-expands-before-expected-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 01:33:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着Boj Rate越来越大的债券损失，日本债券损失在全球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/japan-confronts-biggest-bond-loss-globally-as-boj-rate-hikes-upend-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本银行在过去一年中，日本银行对息税率上涨的枢纽之后，投资者正在重新考虑日本主权债券的策略，这引发了全球债务市场的最大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/japan-confronts-biggest-bond-loss-globally-as-boj-rate-hikes-upend-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 23:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
